data.comment: Today's referee, Lothar D'Hondt, has blown to start the match.
Oud-Heverlee awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 3, Lothar D'Hondt awards the away team a throw-in.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
The match at Den Dreef Stadium has been interrupted briefly for a check on Nils Schouterden, who is down injured.
In the minute 7, Ball goes out of play for a Eupen goal kick.
Nils Schouterden is back on his feet again.
Oud-Heverlee drive upfield and Olivier Myny gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Eupen defender.
In the minute 8, Oud-Heverlee have been awarded a corner by Lothar D'Hondt.
Xavier Mercier (Oud-Heverlee) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Corner awarded to Oud-Heverlee.
In the minute 9, Oud-Heverlee's Mathieu Maertens breaks free at Den Dreef Stadium. But the strike goes wide of the post.
Eupen have a goal kick.
In Heverlee a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 10, Jordi Amat gets his shot on target but fails to score for Eupen.
Eupen's Carlos Embalo is on target but unsuccessful.
Free kick for Eupen in their own half.
In the minute 12, It's a goal kick for the home team in Heverlee.
Throw-in for Oud-Heverlee at Den Dreef Stadium.
Lothar D'Hondt awards Eupen a goal kick.
In the minute 13, Eupen awarded a free kick in their own half.
It's getting dangerous! Free kick for Eupen close to the penalty box.
Eupen's Knowledge Musona gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Oud-Heverlee defender.
In the minute 18, Lothar D'Hondt signals a Oud-Heverlee throw-in in Eupen's half.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Eupen in their own half.
Free kick for Eupen in the half of Oud-Heverlee.
In the minute 20, Can Eupen get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Oud-Heverlee's half?
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Free kick for Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
In the minute 21, Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Oud-Heverlee.
Eupen to take a throw-in in Oud-Heverlee territory.
Throw-in for Oud-Heverlee in the half of Eupen.
In the minute 27, Throw-in for Eupen in their own half.
Oud-Heverlee awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Corner awarded to Oud-Heverlee.
In the minute 29, In Heverlee Oud-Heverlee drive forward through Mathieu Maertens. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Ball safe as Eupen is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Throw-in Oud-Heverlee.
In the minute 31, Goal kick for Eupen at Den Dreef Stadium.
Jens Cools of Eupen smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
Eupen have been awarded a corner by Lothar D'Hondt.
In the minute 33, Eupen attack but Jens Cools's header doesn't find the target.
Goal kick for Oud-Heverlee at Den Dreef Stadium.
Eupen have been awarded a corner by Lothar D'Hondt.
In the minute 35, Free kick for Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
Eupen's Isaac Nuhu gets in a shot on goal at Den Dreef Stadium. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Corner awarded to Eupen.
In the minute 37, Eupen have been awarded a corner by Lothar D'Hondt.
Eupen's Jonathan Heris gets his shot away but it misses the target.
Oud-Heverlee have a goal kick.
In the minute 38, Oud-Heverlee to take a throw-in in Eupen territory.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Eupen in their own half.
Throw-in for Eupen close to the penalty box.
In the minute 40, Derrick Tshimanga is writhing in pain and play has been suspended for a few moments.
Play has been interrupted briefly in Heverlee to check on David Hubert, who is grimacing with pain.
Derrick Tshimanga is back on the pitch.
In the minute 42, The home team replace Mathieu Maertens with Tom Van Hyfte.
Marc Brys (Oud-Heverlee) is making a first change, with Toon Raemaekers replacing the possibly injured Derrick Tshimanga.
Oud-Heverlee awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 44, Corner awarded to Oud-Heverlee.
Ball goes out of play for a Eupen goal kick.
Free kick Oud-Heverlee.
In the minute 45, David Hubert returns to the field for Oud-Heverlee after picking up a slight injury.
Free kick in a good position for Eupen!
The 1st half is prolonged by 5 minutes of added time.
In the minute 45, In Heverlee Eupen attack through Knowledge Musona. The finish is off target, however.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Heverlee.
Oud-Heverlee awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 45, Oud-Heverlee have been awarded a corner by Lothar D'Hondt.
The whistle has gone to end the first-half.
The second-half has started.
In the minute 46, Free kick for Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
Throw-in for Oud-Heverlee in the half of Eupen.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
In the minute 48, Oud-Heverlee awarded a free kick in their own half.
At Den Dreef Stadium, Isaac Nuhu has been yellow-carded for the away team.
Konan N'Dri for Eupen gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
In the minute 49, Lothar D'Hondt awards Oud-Heverlee a goal kick.
Can Eupen get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Oud-Heverlee's half?
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
In the minute 50, Ball safe as Oud-Heverlee is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Free kick Oud-Heverlee.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a Oud-Heverlee throw-in in Eupen's half.
In the minute 53, In Heverlee, Stef Peeters of Eupen is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
Throw-in Oud-Heverlee.
Free kick for Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
In the minute 55, Eupen needs to be cautious. Oud-Heverlee have an attacking throw-in.
Stef Peeters (Eupen) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Corner awarded to Eupen.
In the minute 56, Lothar D'Hondt awards Oud-Heverlee a goal kick.
Free kick for Oud-Heverlee in the half of Eupen.
Eupen's Stef Peeters has been booked in Heverlee.
In the minute 57, Goal! Sascha Kotysch gives Oud-Heverlee a 1-0 lead in Heverlee.
Xavier Mercier instrumental with a fine assist.
Can Eupen get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Oud-Heverlee's half?
In the minute 59, Eupen awarded a free kick in their own half.
Olivier Myny for Oud-Heverlee has been booked by Lothar D'Hondt and receives a first yellow card.
Eupen have a dangerous throw-in.
In the minute 61, Eupen are caught offside.
Oud-Heverlee will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Eupen.
Throw-in for Oud-Heverlee at Den Dreef Stadium.
In the minute 63, Lothar D'Hondt awards the away team a throw-in.
Eupen's Isaac Nuhu breaks free at Den Dreef Stadium. But the strike goes wide of the post.
Ball goes out of play for a Oud-Heverlee goal kick.
In the minute 64, A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Throw-in for Oud-Heverlee in the half of Eupen.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Eupen in their own half.
In the minute 66, Eupen to take a throw-in in Oud-Heverlee territory.
Konan N'Dri (Eupen) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 67, Eupen have been awarded a corner by Lothar D'Hondt.
Eupen's Konan N'Dri gets his shot away but it misses the target.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Heverlee.
Benat San Jose Gil is making the team's first substitution at Den Dreef Stadium with Julien Ngoy replacing Carlos Embalo.
In the minute 68, Throw-in for Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
Isaac Nuhu is on target to level the scores at 1-1.
Eupen pushes forward through Konan N'Dri, whose finish on goal is saved.
In the minute 73, Throw-in for Eupen at Den Dreef Stadium.
Eupen's Knowledge Musona misses with an attempt on goal.
Oud-Heverlee have a goal kick.
In the minute 75, Lothar D'Hondt signals a Eupen throw-in in Oud-Heverlee's half.
Eupen drives forward and Julien Ngoy gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
In Heverlee Eupen attack through Isaac Nuhu. The finish is off target, however.
In the minute 75, Goal kick for Oud-Heverlee at Den Dreef Stadium.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Eupen.
Can Eupen get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Oud-Heverlee's half?
In the minute 77, Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Eupen just outside Oud-Heverlee's area.
Konan N'Dri (Eupen) gets up for a header but cannot keep the ball on target.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Heverlee.
In the minute 78, Throw-in Eupen.
Goal kick for Oud-Heverlee at Den Dreef Stadium.
Eupen have a goal kick.
In the minute 81, Oud-Heverlee's David Hubert goes close with his head but his effort is blocked.
Throw-in for Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
Lothar D'Hondt waits before resuming play because Kenneth Schuermans for Oud-Heverlee is still down.
In the minute 82, Isaac Nuhu is down and play has been interrupted for a few moments.
Oud-Heverlee's Kenneth Schuermans is back in action after a slight knock.
The home team has substituted Kenneth Schuermans with Pierre-Yves Ngawa. Marc Brys is thus making his third change.
In the minute 85, Isaac Nuhu has recovered and rejoins the match in Heverlee.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a free kick to Oud-Heverlee in their own half.
Stef Peeters of Eupen gets in a strike, but is off target.
In the minute 86, Ball goes out of play for a Oud-Heverlee goal kick.
Lothar D'Hondt signals a throw-in for Eupen, close to Oud-Heverlee's area.
Konan N'Dri (Eupen) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 88, Oud-Heverlee push upfield but Lothar D'Hondt quickly pulls them for offside.
Julien Ngoy (Eupen) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Corner awarded to Eupen.
At Den Dreef Stadium the fourth official shows that 6 minutes will be added to the 2nd half.
Nils Schouterden for Eupen gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Lothar D'Hondt awards Oud-Heverlee a goal kick.
Free kick for Eupen in their own half.
Julien Ngoy (Eupen) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Corner awarded to Eupen.
Throw-in for Eupen in the half of Oud-Heverlee.
Can Eupen capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Oud-Heverlee's half?
Oud-Heverlee awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Full-time! The final score is 1-1.
